rdf:Description.lla:note: Note from the Master in the Official Log, stating that William Ridgeway was not able to perform the duties expected of an Able Seaman. The Master states that he has 'no knowledge whatever of repairing sails' and further states that he had 'many times been obligied to turn him off the wheel in consequence of his bad steering'. Ridgeway was subsequently demoted to the role of Ordinary Seaman. See Log Book for full details.
